name: Octave Up
details:
Green Ringer clone"Green Ringer" clone "octave up" pedal from boutique builder Chicago Stompworks. The sound comes from a 60's era transistor circuit that recreates the "Purple Haze" solo effect. It's glitchy, dirty, vintage, not suitable for bass guitar, not intended as a fuzz box although it can do some way-out transistor grind... This one is an all-out space cadet.
-handbuilt boutique quality throughout
-true bypass wiring
-best in class Neutrik brand jacks
-standard center negative "Boss style"9v jack or internal battery
